msgid "Thesis alignment: data analysis and neural prediction"
msgstr "Thesis alignment: data analysis and neural prediction"

msgid ""
"This module implements the core of the diploma topic: aggregated signals (fatigue, surveys, LMS activity, "
"historical load) are combined into a feature vector per time slot; a TensorFlow/Keras model (when trained) "
"or a deterministic fallback scores how «unsuitable» each slot is for intensive teaching. Those scores feed "
"soft penalties in greedy placement, local improvement, and the genetic optimiser — so the timetable is not "
"only feasible but biased away from slots such as Monday early morning when the model predicts high burden."
msgstr ""
"This module implements the core of the diploma topic: aggregated signals (fatigue, surveys, LMS activity, "
"historical load) are combined into a feature vector per time slot; a TensorFlow/Keras model (when trained) "
"or a deterministic fallback scores how «unsuitable» each slot is for intensive teaching. Those scores feed "
"soft penalties in greedy placement, local improvement, and the genetic optimiser — so the timetable is not "
"only feasible but biased away from slots such as Monday early morning when the model predicts high burden."

